feat: build animated landing for Quitamanchas Portátil

Modern, motion-driven one-product landing connected for sale via WhatsApp
checkout (bridge until Culqi is approved).

Sections:
- Header with sticky glass blur on scroll
- Hero with animated product showcase (floating stains erased into product)
- Stat bar with social proof (4.4 rating, +1000 clients, 24h shipping, 7d guarantee)
- How It Works (3 animated steps)
- Benefits grid (6 cards with stagger animations)
- Pricing (3 plans: 1u / pack 2 / pack 3, highlighting middle)
- Testimonials (3 reviews with star ratings)
- FAQ accordion (6 entries)
- Footer with brand, links, contact, social icons
- Sticky mobile CTA bar (visible after scrolling)
- Order modal (form + WhatsApp redirect with pre-filled order)

Tech:
- motion v12 (formerly framer-motion) for all animations
- lucide-react icons
- react-hook-form + zod for order form validation
- Custom Button, Container, Badge UI primitives
- Brand color tokens in globals.css (warm off-white + vibrant orange #FF5722)
- siteConfig and product config centralized in src/lib

Notes:
- Product images are stylized SVG placeholder in ProductShowcase. Replace
